    <!-- ══ IT ADMIN DEPLOYMENT (collapsible) ════════════════════════════ -->
    <details class="admin-deploy">
      <summary>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="17" height="17" style="flex-shrink:0;color:var(--red)">
          <path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
        </svg>
        IT Admin — Mass Deployment Guide
        <svg class="chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" width="16" height="16">
          <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
        </svg>
      </summary>

      <div class="admin-body">

        <!-- PowerShell silent deploy -->
        <div class="admin-section">
          <div class="admin-section-title">Windows — PowerShell Silent Deployment</div>
          <p>Download the PS1 script and run it silently on each machine (requires admin). The script installs RustDesk, writes the server config, creates a desktop shortcut, and registers the device with the dashboard.</p>
          <div class="admin-dl-row">
            <a class="admin-dl-link" href="/install/download/windows.ps1" download="InsiderRemote-Setup.ps1">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="14" height="14"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
              InsiderRemote-Setup.ps1
            </a>
            <a class="admin-dl-link" href="/install/download/windows.bat" download="InsiderRemote-Setup.bat">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="14" height="14"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
              InsiderRemote-Setup.bat
            </a>
          </div>
          <p>Run headlessly on a remote machine via <strong>PsExec</strong> or <strong>Invoke-Command</strong>:</p>
          <div class="cmd-block" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div class="cmd-text" id="deploy-psexec">psexec \\TARGETPC -s powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -WindowStyle Hidden -File "\\share\InsiderRemote-Setup.ps1"</div>
            <button class="cmd-copy-btn" id="cpb-psexec" onclick="copyCmd('deploy-psexec','cpb-psexec')">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <div class="cmd-block" style="margin-bottom:0;">
            <div class="cmd-text" id="deploy-invoke">Invoke-Command -ComputerName TARGETPC -ScriptBlock { irm '<%= apiBase %>/install/download/windows.ps1' -OutFile "$env:TEMP\ir.ps1"; powershell -EP Bypass -File "$env:TEMP\ir.ps1" }</div>
            <button class="cmd-copy-btn" id="cpb-invoke" onclick="copyCmd('deploy-invoke','cpb-invoke')">Copy</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MSI / Intune -->
        <div class="admin-section">
          <div class="admin-section-title">Intune / SCCM / Group Policy (MSI)</div>
          <p>Use the MSI package for deployment via Intune (Win32 app), SCCM, or Group Policy Software Installation. Silent install command:</p>
          <div class="cmd-block" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div class="cmd-text" id="deploy-msi">msiexec /i rustdesk-<%= rdVer %>-x86_64.msi /quiet /norestart</div>
            <button class="cmd-copy-btn" id="cpb-msi" onclick="copyCmd('deploy-msi','cpb-msi')">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <p>After install, push the registry keys below via GPO (Computer Configuration → Preferences → Registry) or a follow-up script.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Registry keys -->
        <div class="admin-section">
          <div class="admin-section-title">Registry Keys — Server Configuration</div>
          <p>Set these registry values on each machine to point RustDesk at your server. Path: <code style="font-size:0.78rem;color:#a8d4ff;">HKLM:\SOFTWARE\RustDesk\config</code></p>
          <table class="reg-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Value Name</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Data</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>custom-rendezvous-server</td>
                <td>REG_SZ</td>
                <td><%= domain %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>relay-server</td>
                <td>REG_SZ</td>
                <td><%= domain %>:21117</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>key</td>
                <td>REG_SZ</td>
                <td><%= publicKey %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>api-server</td>
                <td>REG_SZ</td>
                <td><%= apiBase %></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <div style="margin-top:12px;">
            <div class="cmd-block" style="margin-bottom:0;">
              <div class="cmd-text" id="deploy-reg">$r='HKLM:\SOFTWARE\RustDesk\config'
if(-not(Test-Path $r)){New-Item -Path $r -Force|Out-Null}
Set-ItemProperty -Path $r -Name 'custom-rendezvous-server' -Value '<%= domain %>'
Set-ItemProperty -Path $r -Name 'relay-server'             -Value '<%= domain %>:21117'
Set-ItemProperty -Path $r -Name 'key'                       -Value '<%= publicKey %>'
Set-ItemProperty -Path $r -Name 'api-server'                -Value '<%= apiBase %>'</div>
              <button class="cmd-copy-btn" id="cpb-reg" onclick="copyCmd('deploy-reg','cpb-reg')">Copy</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Linux bulk -->
        <div class="admin-section">
          <div class="admin-section-title">Linux — Ansible / SSH Bulk Deploy</div>
          <p>Push via SSH or Ansible. The script is idempotent — safe to re-run:</p>
          <div class="cmd-block" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div class="cmd-text" id="deploy-ssh">ssh user@host "curl -fsSL '<%= apiBase %>/install/download/linux.sh' | sudo bash"</div>
            <button class="cmd-copy-btn" id="cpb-ssh" onclick="copyCmd('deploy-ssh','cpb-ssh')">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <p>Ansible task snippet:</p>
          <div class="cmd-block" style="margin-bottom:0;">
            <div class="cmd-text" id="deploy-ansible">- name: Install InsiderRemote client
  shell: curl -fsSL '<%= apiBase %>/install/download/linux.sh' | bash
  args:
    creates: /usr/bin/rustdesk</div>
            <button class="cmd-copy-btn" id="cpb-ansible" onclick="copyCmd('deploy-ansible','cpb-ansible')">Copy</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Ports -->
        <div class="admin-section">
          <div class="admin-section-title">Firewall — Required Ports</div>
          <p>Ensure these ports are reachable from client machines to <strong><%= domain %></strong>. All connections are outbound from the client — no inbound rules needed on client machines.</p>
          <table class="reg-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Port</th><th>Protocol</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>21115</td><td>TCP</td><td>NAT type test</td></tr>
              <tr><td>21116</td><td>TCP + UDP</td><td>ID registration &amp; hole-punching</td></tr>
              <tr><td>21117</td><td>TCP</td><td>Relay (encrypted traffic)</td></tr>
              <tr><td>443</td><td>TCP (HTTPS)</td><td>Dashboard API &amp; device registration</td></tr>
